features: 【Large Capacity 10 Tier Narrow Shoe Rack】The 10 tier shoe organizer can store up to 20-25 pairs of adult shoes, and you can remove one layer to fit long boots. This shoe organizer is not only suitable for shoes, but also for bags, toys, towels, sundries, books, plants and small accessories. Shoe storage with 5 hooks, you can hang keys, umbrellas, bags, etc., very practical design.

【Sturdy Material & Compact Structure】The tall shoe rack is made of durable waterproof non-woven fabric layers, reinforced plastic connectors and thickened iron pipes, good stability and prevents rust, The shoe rack closet can hold larger and heavier shoes or objects. The shoe organizer has the characteristics of firmness, stability, and long life.

【High-quality Entrance Shoe Rack】Dimensions of shoe storage: 17"L x 10"W x68"H, simple and elegant appearance. The tall narrow shoe rack can help you make better use of the small space, not only for placing shoes, but also for books and sundries etc. The compact narrow shoe rack is ideal for closets, entryways, dorms, apartments, hallways, closets, and also as a garage shoe shelf for small spaces.

【Easy to Assemble】No tools required, just use the provided parts to manually assemble the unit, which brings you great convenience. Hold the shoes of all family members and keep them organized, you can also split into 5 tier shoe racks 2 units, or order 2 shoe racks and combine them into 1 large shoe rack.

【Worry-Free Service】Any quality problems and problems with our narrow shoe rack after purchase, please contact after-sales service, we will provide you with free parts, replace with new products, or refund.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars For my girls
reviews.reviewText: I purchased two of these shelves for my young daughters. They share a bedroom and have a lot of shoes. These fit perfectly side by side in a small section of wall where not much else could fit there. It holds a lot of shoes and is fairly sturdy. It has helped my girls keep their shoes more organized and put away and not on their floors.The shelves do take a little while to put together. They're not difficult to put together but do take some time. It's definitely important to pay attention to the direction you put the fabric shelf pieces in because they are sewn one way or the other and if you'd like your shelf to look the most cohesive, don't get them flipped.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Just got this today. Went together really easy, lots of pieces, so plan 20 minutes to put together. But when assembled it’s sold. Not very flashy in appearance but Great for a closet.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Totally worth it!!
reviews.reviewText: Totally worth the price. It is tall, fits my walk in closet nicely, holds 2 pairs of shoes on each level, easy to assemble. As a stand-alone, it is not level or very sturdy. It feels like it could topple over easily. But my handy husband had some zip ties with tabs to screw into the wall. We placed 4 screws to keep it level and in place. Now it feels sturdy and is working great!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 30, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Fits perfectly in my closet. Pretty easy to put together. Nice for the price!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality for price
reviews.reviewText: Easy to assemble and sturdy enough for shoes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for toy storage!
reviews.reviewText: I’ve been looking for a way to store my son’s toys in a way that he can see all of them and access them if he wants. This is a great storage solution. It also would be great for many other items. it seems very sturdy but I wouldn’t use it if your child is still of the age where he or she would try to climb it. Another option is to only build them up halfway and have two smaller shelves. Fits perfectly in a small space. Thinking about buying another!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for a small space
reviews.reviewText: This was so easy to put together that I accomplished it in 10 minutes ......... probably could have done it more quickly but I put one shelf on backward and had to do it over. It is not the sturdiest of shelves but holds 10 pair of women's shoes (I only used 5 shelves) very nicely. I'm using it in a temporary location and am sure it will be easy to disassemble when I move.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 5, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Easy to put together and much more sturdy than I expected because it is very light weight.

reviews.reviewTitle: Decent shoe rack for the price
reviews.reviewText: Decent shoe rack made of low quality materials. When installing the metal bars, be careful not to use too much strength or else you'll bend the metal bars in half - which I've done accidentally. The kit comes with a few extra small pieces, but no extra small side horizontal bar nor an extra fabric shelf.Seller also forgot to include the hooks, which they later sent to me in a separate package. Would buy again if the price were a bit lower.
